Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper discusses visual attention mechanisms and their use in self-driving vehicles. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of deep neural control networks and their training on large datasets. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper discusses the training of an end-to-end vehicle controller. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of deep neural control networks in self-driving vehicles. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of natural language advice to augment training data.
